  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
 -->
 <ext_description linkend="Justification_arm.Assumption">
 <p> 
  An <b>Assumption</b> is the identification of something assumed to be 
  true without proof.
 </p> 
 <p>
  The reason or justification for an assumption being made shall be 
  represented by a
  <express_ref linkend="justification:arm:Justification_arm.Justification_assignment"/>
  being assigned to the <b>Assumption</b>.  
 </p>
  <example>
   An activity is planned based on the assumption that the resource required to perform the 
   activity is available at a location.
  </example>
  <p>
   The item that is assumed shall be related to the  <b>Assumption</b>
   by an
   <express_ref linkend="justification:arm:Justification_arm.Assumption_assignment"/>
  </p>
 </ext_description>
